text: laser lessons learned today: pdf is your friend in terms of getting mixed files containing both vector and raster graphics from illustrator to laser via inkscape maintaining alignment
in terms of the 2 color acrylic: mask off for cutting. multiple passes seems to ablate less material or maybe it doesn't catch the masking on fire
I'm doing 3 passes at 10mA which seems to work well
black on white is probably the worst case for vaporized acrylic deposition
